{"text":"1. (Bu bir) suradir. 
Biz uni nozil qildik. Biz uni farz qildik. 
Biz unda ochiq-oydin oyatlarni nozil qildik. 
Shoyadki, eslasangiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,133]}]}

{"text":"2. Zinokor ayol va zinokor erkak, \nikkovlaridan har birini yuz darradan uring. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,79]}]}

{"text":"Agar siz Allohga va oxirat kuniga iymon \nkeltiradigan bo`lsangiz, sizlarni ularga nisbatan Allohning dinida shafqat tutmasin. Va ularning azobiga bir toifa mo`minlar guvoh bo`lsinlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,183]}]}

{"text":"3. Zinokor erkak faqat zinokor yoki mushrika ayolga nikohlanur. Zinokor ayolga faqat zinokor yoki mushrik erkak nikohlanur. Bu, mo`minlarga harom qilinmishdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,159]}]}

{"text":"4. Pokiza ayollarga (bo`hton) toshi otib, 
so`ngra to`rtta guvoh keltira olmaganlarni 
sakson darra uringlar va ularning guvohligini 
abadiy qabul qilmanglar. Ana o`shalar fosiqlardir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,184]}]}

{"text":"5. Magar bundan keyin tavba qilib, \no`zini isloh qilganlar (mustasnodir). \nZero, Alloh o`ta mag`firatli va o`ta rahimlidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,123]}]}

{"text":"6. O`z juftlariga (bo`hton) toshi otib, \nfaqat o`zlaridan boshqa guvohlari bo`lmaganlar esa, bas, ulardan har birining guvohligi Allohning nomi ila to`rt marta, albatta, u rostgo`ylardan ekanligi haqida shohidlik berishdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,223]}]}

{"text":"7. Beshinchisida esa, agar yolg`onchilardan bo`lsa, unga Allohning la'nati bo`lishini (aytishlikdir).","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,101]}]}

{"text":"8. Va u(ayol)dan azobni qaytaradigan narsa Allohning nomi ila to`rt marta, albatta, \nu(er) yolg`onchilardandir, deb shohidlik berishidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,137]}]}

{"text":"9. Beshinchisida esa, agar u(er) rostgo`ylardan bo`lsa, o`zi(ayol)ga Allohning g`azabi bo`lishini (aytishlikdir).","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,113]}]}

{"text":"10. Agar sizlarga Allohning fazli va marhamati \nbo`lmaganida... Albatta, Alloh tavbalarni ko`plab qabul qilguvchi va o`ta hikmatli zot bo`lmaganida edi...","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,154]}]}

{"text":"11. Albatta, ifkni keltirganlar o`zingizdan bo`lgan \nbir usba (to`da)dir. Uni o`zingizga yomonlik deb hisoblamang. Aksincha, u siz uchun yaxshilikdir. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,151]}]}

{"text":"Ulardan har bir kishi uchun o`zi qilgan kasbning gunohi bordir. Ulardan (gunohning) kattasini \nko`targan kimsaga buyuk azob bordir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,131]}]}

{"text":"12. U(ifk)ni eshitgan vaqtingizda mo`minlar va \nmo`minalar o`zlari haqida yaxshi gumonga borib: \nBu ochiq-oydin ifk-ku! desalar bo`lmasmidi?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,143]}]}

{"text":"13. U(ifkchi)lar o`sha(ifk)ga to`rtta guvoh \nkeltirsalar bo`lmasmidi?! Bas, guvohlarni keltira olmagan chog`da ana o`shalar o`zlari \nAllohning huzurida yolg`onchidirlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,169]}]}

{"text":"14. Agar dunyoyu oxiratda sizlarga 
Allohning fazli, marhamati bo`lmaganida, 
o`zingiz ichiga sho`ng`igan narsa uchun sizni, 
albatta, buyuk azob tutar edi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,156]}]}

{"text":"15. O`shanda siz u(ifk)ni tillaringiz ila ilib olar, 
og`zingiz ila o`zingiz bilmagan narsani gapirar 
edingiz va u (ifk)ni o`zingizga yengil sanardingiz. 
Holbuki, u Allohning nazdida buyukdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,194]}]}

{"text":"16. Uni eshitgan chog`ingizda: Bizga buni \ngapirmog`imiz to`g`ri kelmas. O`zing poksan! \nBu katta bo`htondir! desangiz bo`lmasmidi?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,134]}]}

{"text":"17. Agar mo`min bo`lsangiz, \nhargiz u(ifk)ga o`xshash narsaga qaytmasligingizni Alloh sizga va'z-nasihat qilur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,111]}]}

{"text":"18. Alloh sizga oyatlarni bayon qilur. \nVa Alloh o`ta bilguvchi, o`ta hikmatli Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,86]}]}

{"text":"19. Albatta, iymon keltirganlar ichida 
fohisha tarqalishini yaxshi ko`radiganlarga 
bu dunyoyu oxiratda alamli azob bordir. 
Alloh biladir, sizlar bilmassizlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,161]}]}

{"text":"20. Agar sizlarga Allohning fazli, \nmarhamati bo`lmaganida... Va, albatta, \nAlloh o`ta shafqatli va rahimli bo`lmaganida...","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,123]}]}

{"text":"Kim shaytonning izidan ergashsa, bas, \nalbatta, u fohisha va munkarga buyuradir. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,81]}]}

{"text":"Agar sizlarga Allohning fazli va marhamati \nbo`lmaganida, abadul-abad ichingizdan biror kishi poklana olmas edi. Lekin Alloh O`zi xohlagan kishini poklar. Alloh o`ta eshitguvchi, o`ta bilguvchi Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,201]}]}

{"text":"22. Sizlardan fazl va boylik egasi bo`lganlar qarindoshlarga, miskinlarga va Allohning yo`lida muhojir bo`lganlarga (nafaqa) bermaslikka qasam ichmasinlar, bas, afv etsinlar, o`tib yuborsinlar. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,194]}]}

{"text":"Alloh sizlarni mag`firat qilishini xush ko`rmaysizlarmi?! Alloh o`ta mag`firatli, o`ta rahimli Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,102]}]}

{"text":"23. Albatta, pokiza, g`ofila va mo`mina ayollarga \n(bo`hton) toshi otganlar bu dunyoyu oxiratda\n la'natlanurlar. Ularga katta azob bordur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,138]}]}

{"text":"24. U kunda tillari, qo`llari va oyoqlari qilib yurgan amallari haqida ularga qarshi guvohlik berur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,100]}]}

{"text":"25. O`sha kunda Alloh ularning haq jazolarini to`liq berur va ular Allohning O`zi ochiq haq ekanini bilurlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,109]}]}

{"text":"26. Nopok xotinlar nopok erkaklar uchundir. 
Nopok erkaklar nopok xotinlar uchundir. 
Pokiza ayollar pokiza erkaklar uchundir. 
Pokiza erkaklar pokiza ayollar uchundir. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,169]}]}

{"text":"Ana o`shalar u(bo`htonchi)lar aytayotgan narsalardan poklangandirlar. \nUlarga mag`firat va go`zal rizq bordir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,110]}]}

{"text":"27. Ey, iymon keltirganlar! O`z uylaringizdan boshqa uylarga to izn so`ramaguningizcha va ularning ahliga salom bermaguningizcha, kirmang. Ana shunday qilmog`ingiz siz uchun yaxshidir, shoyadki, eslasangiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,206]}]}

{"text":"28. Bas, agar u(uy)larda birortani topmasangiz, to sizga izn berilmaguncha, ularga kirmang. Agar sizga, qayting, deyilsa, bas, qayting, o`sha siz uchun pokdir. Alloh nima amal qilayotganingizni o`ta bilguvchidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,212]}]}

{"text":"29. Maskan bo`lmagan, siz uchun foyda bor uylarga \n(iznsiz) kirishingizda gunoh yo`qdir. Alloh nimani oshkor qilayotganingizni va nimani yashirin qilayotganingizni biladir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,172]}]}

{"text":"30. Sen mo`minlarga ayt, ko`zlarini tiysinlar va farjlarini saqlasinlar. Ana shu ular uchun pokdir. Albatta, Alloh nima hunar qilayotganlaridan xabardordir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,156]}]}

{"text":"31. Sen mo`minalarga ayt: Ko`zlarini tiysinlar, \nfarjlarini saqlasinlar va ziynatlarini ko`rsatmasinlar, magar zohir bo`lgan ziynatlar bo`lsa (mayli). \nRo`mollarini ko`ksilariga to`sib yursinlar. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,197]}]}

{"text":"Ziynatlarini ko`rsatmasinlar, 
magar erlariga yo otalariga yo erlarining otalariga 
yo o`g`illariga yo erlarining o`g`illariga 
yo aka-ukalariga yo aka-ukalarining o`g`illariga 
yo opa-singillarining o`g`illariga yo ayollariga ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,227]}]}

{"text":"yo o`z qo`llarida mulk bo`lganlarga yo (ayollarga) behojat erkak xizmatchilarga yo ayollar avratining farqiga bormagan yosh bolalarga (bo`lsa, mayli). ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,151]}]}

{"text":"Maxfiy ziynatlarini bildirish uchun \noyoqlarini (erga) urmasinlar. \nAllohga barchangiz tavba qiling, ey mo`minlar! Shoyadki, najot topsangizlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,145]}]}

{"text":"32. Oralaringizdagi nikohsizlarni va\n qulu cho`rilaringizdan solihlarini nikohlab qo`ying. Agar faqir bo`lsalar, Alloh ularni O`z fazlidan boy qilur. Alloh (fazli) keng, o`ta bilguvchi Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,192]}]}

{"text":"33. Nikoh(imkon)ni topa olmaganlar, to Alloh ularni \nO`z fazlidan boy qilgunicha, iffatlarini saqlasinlar. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,107]}]}

{"text":"Qo`llaringizda mulk bo`lganlardan (ozodlik) \nvasiqasini istaydiganlari bo`lsa, bas, ularda yaxshilik borligini bilsangiz, ular ila vasiqa yozing va \nAllohning sizga bergan molidan ularga bering. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,195]}]}

{"text":"Hayoti dunyoning o`tkinchi matohini istab, \npoklikni iroda qilgan (cho`ri) qizlaringizni \nfohishalikka majbur qilmang. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,119]}]}

{"text":"Kim ularni majbur qilgan bo`lsa, bas, albatta, \nAlloh ular majbur qilganlaridan keyin o`ta \nmag`firatli va rahimli Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,122]}]}

{"text":"34. Batahqiq, Biz sizlarga ochiq-oydin oyatlarni, sizdan oldin o`tganlardan misolni va taqvodorlar uchun va'zni nozil qildik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,125]}]}

{"text":"35. Alloh osmonlar va yerning nuridir. \nUning nurining misoli xuddi bir tokcha, uning ichiga chiroq qo`yilgan, chiroq esa, shisha ichida, ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,138]}]}

{"text":"shisha esa, go`yo durdan bo`lgan bir yulduz bo`lib, sharqiy ham, g`arbiy ham bo`lmagan muborak zaytun daraxtidan yoqiladir. Uning moyi o`ziga olov tegmasa ham, yoritib yuboray deydir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,183]}]}

{"text":" (Bu) nur ustiga nurdir. 
Alloh xohlagan odamni O`z nuriga hidoyat qilur. 
Alloh odamlarga misollarni keltirur. 
Alloh har bir narsani o`ta bilguvchidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,153]}]}

{"text":"36. (U) bir uylardaki, Alloh ularning ko`tarilishiga va ularda O`z ismi zikr qilinishiga izn bergandir. \nUlarda Unga ertayu kech tasbih ayturlar","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,144]}]}

{"text":"37. Bir kishilarki, ularni tijorat ham, oldi-sotdi ham Allohning zikridan, namozni to`kis ado etishdan va zakot berishdan mashg`ul qila olmas. Ular qalblar va ko`zlar iztirobga tushadigan kundan qo`rqarlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,206]}]}

{"text":"38. Alloh ularni qilgan amallarining eng go`zali ila mukofotlashi va fazli karamidan ziyoda qilib berishi uchundir. Alloh xohlagan kishiga behisob rizq berur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,158]}]}

{"text":"39. Kufr keltirganlarning amallari sahrodagi sarobga o`xshar. Chanqoq odam uni suv deb hisoblar. Qachonki, uning oldiga kelsa, hech narsani topmas. Va u oldida Allohni topur. Bas, U zot uning hisobini \nto`liq qilur. Alloh o`ta tez hisob qilguvchidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,250]}]}

{"text":"40. Yoki xuddi qa'rsiz dengizdagi zulmatlarga o`xshar. Uning ustidan mavj qoplagandir, u(mavj)ning ham ustidan mavj va uni esa, bulut (qoplagandir). ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,149]}]}

{"text":"Bir-birining ustidagi zulmatlardir. \nU qo`lini chiqarsa, ko`ra olmas. \nKimgaki Alloh nur bermasa, uning uchun nur bo`lmas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,122]}]}

{"text":"41. Allohga osmonlar va yerdagi bor jonzot va 
saf tortgan holidagi qushlar tasbih aytishini ham 
ko`rmaysanmi?! Har biri o`z duosi va tasbihini, batahqiq, bilmishdir. Alloh nima amal qilishlarini 
o`ta bilguvchidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,216]}]}

{"text":"42. Osmonlar va yerning mulki Allohnikidir va \nqaytish ham faqat Allohgadir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,76]}]}

{"text":"43. Alloh bulutlarni haydashini,
